Nnenna Egwuekwe (amụrụ na Septemba 22, 1992), nke a maara dịka Nenny B, bụ onye mgbasa ozi Naijiria. Ọ bụ VJ ugbu a maka MTV Base Africa.
Nenny B si Imo Steeti ma amụọ ya na Lagos Steeti, Naịjirịa. Ọ gara Aloysius Ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị, Abuja maka agụmakwụkwọ ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị ya ma nwee agụmakwụkwọ sekọndrị ya n'otu Abuja
Ọ gakwara Mahadum Chukwuemeka Odumegwu Ojukwu ebe ọ nwetara akara ugo mmụta na Bekee naNkwukọrịta Mass, tupu ọ gaa Mahadum Wollongong maka nzere masta ya.
Nenny B malitere ọrụ ya na 2007 mgbe ọ malitere ịpụta n'ọkwa na 2007 Kora Awards, na-emeghe ihe nkiri maka 50 Cent

N'afọ 2009, ọ gara n'ihu na ụlọ ọrụ mgbasa ozi, dị ka onye na-arụ ọrụ maka Africa Independent Television, AIT, na ihe ngosi "Ihe na-ebilite". Ọ bịara n'ihu na 2012 wee gaa n'ihu n'afọ 2014 maka arụmọrụ ya na ihe ngosi Reality TV, X Factor West Africa na Star the Winner Is

Ọ sonyeere News Agency nke Nigeria, NAN dị ka onye nta akụkọ ma rụọ ọrụ na nkà nhazi ya, tupu o mesịa bụrụ onye nchịkọta akụkọ. N'afọ 2014, ọ sonyeere Hot 98.3 FM dị ka onye na-elekọta Daily Drive Time Show na Battle Of The Sexes
N'afọ 2017, Radio Magazine debere ya n'ihu ya, na-egosi ya n'elu ndepụta ya "Top 20 Best Radio Presenters in Nigeria"

Ọ kwadoro Agbamakwụkwọ m ukwu Naijiria, La Belle Africa, Trace Afrobeat Show, Johnnie Walker Jazz & Whiskey Night, AMVCA After Party, Jamrock, Celeb Living. N'ọnwa Nọvemba 2017, ọ ghọrọ onye nnọchi anya ụlọ ọrụ Nkataa. Ọ na-arụ ọrụ ugbu a dị ka VJ maka MTV Base Africa, kemgbe 2018.
